    "body": "Thanks @tomcbean :) \r\n\r\n@quantumproducer At the moment, the solc version is tightly coupled with the truffle version. See the [releases](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases) to get the one you need. \r\n\r\n`Migrations.sol` is maintained as part of a separate `truffle-box` and needs to work with multiple versions of the compiler, so we're letting it float lower than latest solc. See #931 for more detail on this. \r\n\r\n",
